*[[Yeghishe Charents]] (1897<U+2013>1937), Armenian poet
*[[Hovhannes Zardaryan]] (1918<U+2013>1992), Armenian painter
*[[Kelime Ayd<U+0131>n <U+00C7>etinkaya]] (1982), cross country skier
*[[G<U+00FC>ls<U+00FC>m Tatar]] (1983), world and European champion female boxer
*[[Ca<U+011F>la <U+015E>ikel]] - famous Turkish actress and model 1997 [[Miss Turkey]] winner of Azerbaijani descent
*[[H<U+00FC>lya Av<U+015F>ar]] - famous Turkish actress, pop folk singer, businesswoman, columnist, fashion designer, magazine editor, professional tennis player, and former beauty pageant titleholder
*[[Yavuz Bing<U+00F6>l]] - famous Turkish folk music singer and an actor
